snippet.textDisplay:
Dear coke studio I love this song , love the fusion nd as a music listener I can hear it on loop, But when it comes to holi , we want music where we can dance for hours non stop , and people may love hip hop but not everyone at a society holi functions gonna dance on a song, where rap is included.. (for eg. : Kaala chasma the rap part is so nicely fused that it doesn't interrupt while dancing but in this song it does) it's just my personal opinion as I wanted to play this  while my family was having fun in Brij itself, but the rap part, I had to change the song or skip that part so that we could dance wo interruption, idk if it make  sense to you but a Song named " Aj Braj m holi re rasiya" didn't work in Braj itself and failed me.

That's it.  And Yes expecting more of maithili thakur she took our heart ❤️❤️❤️❤️ with everything she do.
snippet.textOriginal:

(for eg. : Kaala chasma the rap part is so nicely fused that it doesn't interrupt while dancing but in this song it does) it's just my personal opinion as I wanted to play this  while my family was having fun in Brij itself, but the rap part, I had to change the song or skip that part so that we could dance wo interruption, idk if it make  sense to you but a Song named " Aj Braj m holi re rasiya" didn't work in Braj itself and failed me.

That's it.  And Yes expecting more of maithili thakur she took our heart ❤️❤️❤️❤️ with everything she do.
